                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0c4a62dd-c525-4249-96e2-466a45d278e1",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For the next two classes, we will construct combat runestones that create fields of magical energy around you. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1cf4a40c-6f3c-4067-bcbf-e301778ea5af",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You say the name of the spell as you place the runestone on the ground. This will create an aura of defensive or offensive magic surrounding you.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4d6e81ad-6d77-47b2-bffa-fa74c663466d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "These runestones not only are inscribed with the essential runes, but they are glazed with colored glass made from the rare sands of the Lost Lake of the Shapeirian Desert.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7b3f989e-cdf2-42f9-aefa-5fbdb4745f6e",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we will make the <i>Frigida</i> runestone. This spell will slow a monster down, reducing its damage and movement. It's particularly effective against cold-blooded creatures like Gogs.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "59d32914-68a3-403c-981c-439b72ec70e1",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any further questions before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "9c40f085-1596-4690-baf3-984a777cdfb4",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "5a73834b-627a-4627-8c5c-d19d2cddeaf4",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "bbdda712-39d4-46bb-b0b5-770e7b8cb2eb",
                            "text": "Ask How a Runestone Affects Monsters",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2a4871a5-40e0-4399-924b-60abd270ccbb",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "How does a runestone work? Does it affect everything around it?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f5b6136b-7a16-4dc9-b54e-33fc94bd3c2e",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This type of runestone generates a magical field around itself. Whenever something moves into that aura, that creature is affected by the spell. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b15fbe83-e437-48ee-b83e-e6ba2409ba62",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, the magical field that powerful cannot be maintained for very long. The runestone will be inactive for several minutes before it can be used again.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "a9120468-c683-4afd-aef2-8f141d8cf69f",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ef5b5643-aff6-42e1-a199-f39b5c747cee",
                            "text": "Ask About the Glaze",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cf3d21ae-ec1c-498b-bfed-5d45f284ab87",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Why do these runestones require special glaze from some desert?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "10abb7d8-9cd6-4c87-a0f7-0cca92f1e9e3",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The translucent glaze creates the magical aura that surrounds the activated runestone. The specific color of the glaze is significant and helps define the spell effect.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "619ccc03-0e6a-40e0-810c-c5eb261d86dc",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "30e0ab62-5649-4180-8558-f0d1f36e9d0b",
                            "text": "Ask a Snarky Question About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fd89b950-ecff-4842-b37f-94f9aa11376c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So why are Wizards always so weird? Are they born odd or does the use of magic make them kookie?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5300bd15-197d-412d-b566-c11d74de022a",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "We Wizards prefer to use the term, 'eccentric.' ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "86b95280-4667-4b57-83e4-22ef85d5b1b8",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizards seldom worry about the opinions of society or the norms of behavior. We behave as we choose to behave, wear what we choose to wear, and associate only the people with whom we care to deal.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a2249dc9-5fa5-4295-9a7f-bb2ca82f28d2",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "We have the opportunity to be as odd as we choose to be. It is delightfully liberating from the constraints and censure of social mores. We simply couldn't care less what others think of us.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "a8155894-6da8-423a-8fde-aed7b3efdf9f",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "32",
